data.description: Imagine moving into a home that still has a full warranty for years to come inside & out. Stress free!!. This completely move in ready home was just built and moved into late 2022 & sellers are being transferred. Property is in immaculate condition. 4 bedroom & 2.5 bath this has plenty of space for living! Large open living to kitchen area, full indoor utility room with washer & dryer to convey! Upstairs has 4 large bedrooms & 2 baths. Huge backyard with completely new fence surrounding and a pool to cool off in this heat when your ready. All set & ready to go to move into stress & hassle free!
